These exercises are taken mainly from winter term 2015/16 and contain basic concepts like pattern matching, lists, tuples, simple sum types, etc.
You should also take another look at exercise sheets 5 and 6 (especially exercise 6.1) (you may skip exercise 6.2 (AVL-tree)) from winter term 2016/17. 

Exercises for validation of expression signatures see 2016/signatures.
